<div id="trans_panel" class="page">
    <table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" class="about_sawce"><tr>
        <td width="25%" class="first" valign="top">Sawce is a platform for distributing DRM-free, high-quality music, and giving artists and fans over 90% of the proceeds from each song sold.</td>
        <td width="25%" valign="top">It's a platform that motivates fans to promote music and visualizes the way it moves: mapping out who's who in the art of social diffusion.</td>
        <td width="25%" valign="top">It's about allowing artists to understand who their fans are so they can connect with them in meaningful ways.</td>
        <td width="25%" valign="top">We believe that music is something that empowered fans can build amazing value around. It's spread with Sawce.</td>
    </tr></table>    
</div>